is a Japanese professional football club in Iwata.
History.
The club was founded in 1970.
The club became J2 in 2013.
Notable achievement.
The team has some notable achievements.
In 2009, Ryoichi Maeda made three goals in one game against Nagoya Grampus.
A match with Shimizu S-Pulse is called Shizuoka Derby.
